msgstr "Quick links"

msgid "Before you start"
msgstr "Before you start"

msgid ""
"You need access to Chat settings before you can import or manage assessment "
"tools in this app."
msgstr ""
"You need access to Chat settings before you can import or manage assessment "
"tools in this app."

msgid "Choose an assessment"
msgstr "Choose an assessment"

msgid ""
"Open Data Capture and select the assessment card you want to work with. The "
"list only shows active assessment tools that are already available in the "
"app."
msgstr ""
"Open Data Capture and select the assessment card you want to work with. The "
"list only shows active assessment tools that are already available in the "
"app."

msgid "Select the program card to open its event list."
msgstr "Select the program card to open its event list."

msgid "Use the event list to review both submitted events and saved drafts."
msgstr "Use the event list to review both submitted events and saved drafts."

msgid "Select the organisation unit"
msgstr "Select the organisation unit"

msgid ""
"Choose the organisation unit before you start a new record. For new "
"records, this selection controls where the event is captured."
msgstr ""
"Choose the organisation unit before you start a new record. For new "
"records, this selection controls where the event is captured."

msgid "Pick the correct facility, district, or branch before continuing."
msgstr "Pick the correct facility, district, or branch before continuing."

msgid ""
"Completed events keep their original organisation unit and do not allow "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"Completed events keep their original organisation unit and do not allow "
"changes."

msgid "Enter the report date"
msgstr "Enter the report date"

msgid ""
"Use the Report date step to enter the date for the assessment. You must "
"complete this step before moving into the form sections."
msgstr ""
"Use the Report date step to enter the date for the assessment. You must "
"complete this step before moving into the form sections."

msgid "The report date is stored as `occurredAt` in the event payload."
msgstr "The report date is stored as `occurredAt` in the event payload."

msgid "If the date field is blank or invalid, the form will not let you continue."
msgstr "If the date field is blank or invalid, the form will not let you continue."

msgid "Complete the form sections"
msgstr "Complete the form sections"

msgid ""
"Move through the section list on the left and fill the required fields in "
"each section. The navigation highlights incomplete required fields."
msgstr ""
"Move through the section list on the left and fill the required fields in "
"each section. The navigation highlights incomplete required fields."

msgid "Required fields must be completed before you can submit the assessment."
msgstr "Required fields must be completed before you can submit the assessment."

msgid "Long section names wrap in the side navigation so you can still read them."
msgstr "Long section names wrap in the side navigation so you can still read them."

msgid "Capture coordinates when needed"
msgstr "Capture coordinates when needed"

msgid ""
"Coordinate fields let you enter latitude and longitude directly, or use the "
"current location button to fill both values automatically."
msgstr ""
"Coordinate fields let you enter latitude and longitude directly, or use the "
"current location button to fill both values automatically."

msgid "You can edit the coordinates after using current location."
msgstr "You can edit the coordinates after using current location."

msgid ""
"Both latitude and longitude must be valid before the field passes "
"validation."
msgstr ""
"Both latitude and longitude must be valid before the field passes "
"validation."

msgid "Save and resume drafts"
msgstr "Save and resume drafts"

msgid ""
"Use Save progress to keep an unfinished record. Drafts are grouped by user "
"and program, and each saved draft stays unique by organisation unit and "
"report date."
msgstr ""
"Use Save progress to keep an unfinished record. Drafts are grouped by user "
"and program, and each saved draft stays unique by organisation unit and "
"report date."

msgid "Open the Drafts tab to continue saved work."
msgstr "Open the Drafts tab to continue saved work."

msgid ""
"Parent organisation units can show drafts from all descendants in the event "
"list."
msgstr ""
"Parent organisation units can show drafts from all descendants in the event "
"list."

msgid "Review submitted events"
msgstr "Review submitted events"

msgid ""
"Use the All view in the event list to review tracker events from the "
"selected organisation unit and all descendants, together with any matching "
"drafts."
msgstr ""
"Use the All view in the event list to review tracker events from the "
"selected organisation unit and all descendants, together with any matching "
"drafts."

msgid "Completed events read directly from the DHIS2 tracker events endpoint."
msgstr "Completed events read directly from the DHIS2 tracker events endpoint."

msgid ""
"The list shows report date, organisation unit name, creator, and updater "
"details when available."
msgstr ""
"The list shows report date, organisation unit name, creator, and updater "
"details when available."

msgid ""
"Use this page as an in-app checklist for selecting an assessment, entering "
"report dates, completing sections, saving drafts, and reviewing submitted "
"events."
msgstr ""
"Use this page as an in-app checklist for selecting an assessment, entering "
"report dates, completing sections, saving drafts, and reviewing submitted "
"events."

msgid ""
"You need at least one active assessment in the app and access to the "
"relevant organisation units before you can capture new data."
msgstr ""
"You need at least one active assessment in the app and access to the "
"relevant organisation units before you can capture new data."

